---
title: Sticky Pork Chops with Apple Stuffing and Creamy Mash
description: Sage and apple stuffed pork chops make for a luxurious weeknight meal. Creamy mash and a sweet pan sauce bring this dish together for a hearty and nostalgic pork dinner!
